content: Let me complete things on the back end and send you another DM. Be back soon!

You have been sending DM's back and forth with me during the onboarding process. All the DM's are in left Upper corner of Discord, game controller icon. Thanks for checking in!
Got it.  Thanks for help getting me up to speed. I now know where it is. Signing off for now. I greatly appreciate ypur patience.
